channel.description:
Thats correct. I've been working on a server lately and these are some of the skillcape emotes I've finished. I only have 1 left to do. These are just a few of them I'm using as examples. I'll get around to adding more later. Thanks.
Please note: These are NOT RS emotes. These were designed by me, not them. The wording are automatic with skillcape emotes.
My Favorite One ;) FiremakingCape

FarmingCape [URL=http://s213.photobucket.com/albums/cc62/vanackNR/?action=view&current=clip0006.flv][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc62/vanackNR/th_clip0006.jpg[/img][/URL]
HPCape [URL=http://s213.photobucket.com/albums/cc62/vanackNR/?action=view&current=clip0007.flv][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc62/vanackNR/th_clip0007.jpg[/img][/URL]
I understand that these are .avi formats. I'm not sure of the extension that I'd need to create a moving image. Sorry. If anyone can help me with that, it would be much appreciated.
Vanack -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
